g.text: The embedded temperature sensor, a specific instance of temperature sensor.
The accuracy of the temperature sensor is +-0.5 °C in normal temperature and humidity conditions.
The capabilities of the temperature sensor in normal temperature and humidity conditions.
The smallest possible time between one observation and the next is 2 s on average.
The precision (= repeatability) of the temperature sensor is +-0.2 °C in normal temperature and humidity conditions.
The sensitivity and resolution of the temperature sensor is 0.1 °C in normal temperature and humidity conditions.
